歟？」曰：「使其尤良者一人焉爾。」「烏知\n      其尤良而使之？」曰：「眾人之所謂尤良者，而隱 1 之以吾心，其可也。夫材不相\n      逮，不相為謀，又相忌也。人之愚不能者常多，而智能者常少，醫者十，愚不能者\n      烏知其不九邪？並使之，一日而病且亡，誰者任 2 其咎邪？」\n      作者在這段文字中雖論使醫治病，但用意卻在談用人治國之理。據此，作者主\n      張在上位者應該如何？\n                                \n      (A)眾口交譽之人，直接任用            1.隱：詳細考量\n      (B)善於汰劣擢優，委賢重任            2.任：擔當、承受\n      (C)務求廣納眾議，興利除弊\n      (D)使愚智不相忌，同心為國\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-031", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "【甲】春雪滿空來，觸處似花開。不知園裡樹，若個 1 是真梅？\n【乙】牆角數枝梅，凌寒獨自開。遙知不是雪，為有暗香來。\n根據甲、乙兩詩的內涵，下列敘述何者最恰當？          ", "options": ["甲詩以梅喻雪，乙詩以雪喻梅               1.若個：哪個", "甲詩主題是詠雪，乙詩主題是詠梅", "兩詩所描繪的都是暮春夜晚的景致", "兩詩作者都無法分辨眼前所見是雪還是梅"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 31, "raw_text": "31. 【甲】春雪滿空來，觸處似花開。不知園裡樹，若個 1 是真梅？\n    【乙】牆角數枝梅，凌寒獨自開。遙知不是雪，為有暗香來。\n    根據甲、乙兩詩的內涵，下列敘述何者最恰當？          \n    (A)甲詩以梅喻雪，乙詩以雪喻梅               1.若個：哪個\n    (B)甲詩主題是詠雪，乙詩主題是詠梅\n    (C)兩詩所描繪的都是暮春夜晚的景致\n    (D)兩詩作者都無法分辨眼前所見是雪還是梅\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-032", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "子胥出逃，邊候 1 得之。子胥曰：「上索我者，以我有美珠也。今我已\n亡之矣，我將謂子取而吞之。」候因釋之。\n根據這段文字，下列敘述何者正確？\n", "options": ["子胥用言語威脅邊候以求自保 1.邊候：邊吏", "子胥以美珠賄賂邊候換取自由", "邊候侵吞子胥的美珠又誣陷他", "邊候相信子胥的清白而釋放他"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 32, "raw_text": "32.\n        子胥出逃，邊候 1 得之。子胥曰：「上索我者，以我有美珠也。今我已\n      亡之矣，我將謂子取而吞之。」候因釋之。\n\n      根據這段文字，下列敘述何者正確？\n                                     \n      (A)子胥用言語威脅邊候以求自保\n                                     1.邊候：邊吏\n      (B)子胥以美珠賄賂邊候換取自由\n      (C)邊候侵吞子胥的美珠又誣陷他\n      (D)邊候相信子胥的清白而釋放他\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-033", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "隋煬帝善屬文 1 ，而不欲人出其右，司隸薛道衡由是得罪。後因事誅\n之，曰：「更能作『空梁落燕泥』否？」\n根據這段文字，可以推知下列何者？\n", "options": ["煬帝命薛道衡作詩，薛因抗命而被殺     1.屬文：連綴字句而成文，", "薛道衡死後，煬帝感嘆再也無人能出其右        指寫文章", "薛道衡因事被誅，臨刑以「空梁」一詩明志", "煬帝嫉妒薛道衡能有「空梁落燕泥」這等佳句"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": null, "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 33, "raw_text": "33.\n        隋煬帝善屬文 1 ，而不欲人出其右，司隸薛道衡由是得罪。後因事誅\n      之，曰：「更能作『空梁落燕泥』否？」\n\n      根據這段文字，可以推知下列何者？\n                              \n      (A)煬帝命薛道衡作詩，薛因抗命而被殺     1.屬文：連綴字句而成文，\n      (B)薛道衡死後，煬帝感嘆再也無人能出其右        指寫文章\n      (C)薛道衡因事被誅，臨刑以「空梁」一詩明志\n      (D)煬帝嫉妒薛道衡能有「空梁落燕泥」這等佳句\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-034", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，下列敘述何者正確？", "options": ["作者在仰光也會穿小一號的拖鞋", "印尼人習慣穿比腳大一號的拖鞋", "雨季時緬甸人喜歡穿小一號的沙龍", "埃及人的正常體溫較其他國家的人高"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-34", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 34, "raw_text": "34. 根據本文，下列敘述何者正確？\n    (A)作者在仰光也會穿小一號的拖鞋\n    (B)印尼人習慣穿比腳大一號的拖鞋\n    (C)雨季時緬甸人喜歡穿小一號的沙龍\n    (D)埃及人的正常體溫較其他國家的人高\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-035", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "畫線處為本文主旨所在，根據前後文意脈絡，填入下列何者最恰當？", "options": ["不懂的事就應該問人，以免成為別人的笑柄", "注重事物的本質，鞋子的實用與否比美觀更加重要", "每個人的欣賞觀點不盡相同，那是和各人的性格有關", "不要用自己的常識來判斷別人，並且尊重在地的生活智慧"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-34", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 35, "raw_text": "35. 畫線處為本文主旨所在，根據前後文意脈絡，填入下列何者最恰當？\n    (A)不懂的事就應該問人，以免成為別人的笑柄\n    (B)注重事物的本質，鞋子的實用與否比美觀更加重要\n    (C)每個人的欣賞觀點不盡相同，那是和各人的性格有關\n    (D)不要用自己的常識來判斷別人，並且尊重在地的生活智慧\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-036", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據這張圖表，下列敘述何者正確？", "options": ["東、西德統一後，開始拆除柏林圍牆", "東、西德從各自建國到統一超過四十年", "蘇聯紅軍占領柏林後就開始興建柏林圍牆", "柏林圍牆拆除後，西柏林人始能造訪東柏林"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 36, "raw_text": "36. 根據這張圖表，下列敘述何者正確？\n    (A)東、西德統一後，開始拆除柏林圍牆\n    (B)東、西德從各自建國到統一超過四十年\n    (C)蘇聯紅軍占領柏林後就開始興建柏林圍牆\n    (D)柏林圍牆拆除後，西柏林人始能造訪東柏林\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-037", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據圖表推論，右列事件發生的先後順序 甲、甘迺迪訪問西柏林\n最可能是何者？            乙、布蘭登堡門關閉", "options": ["甲→乙→丙→丁         丙、雷根當選美國總統", "甲→丁→乙→丙         丁、戈巴契夫下臺", "乙→甲→丙→丁", "乙→丙→甲→丁"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 37, "raw_text": "37. 根據圖表推論，右列事件發生的先後順序 甲、甘迺迪訪問西柏林\n    最可能是何者？            乙、布蘭登堡門關閉\n    (A)甲→乙→丙→丁         丙、雷根當選美國總統\n    (B)甲→丁→乙→丙         丁、戈巴契夫下臺\n    (C)乙→甲→丙→丁\n    (D)乙→丙→甲→丁\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-038", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，下列敘述何者正確？", "options": ["「封」和「禪」在同一處進行", "封禪的目的是為天下萬民祈福", "物富民豐的年代才會舉行封禪", "舉行封禪的皇帝未必賢德英明"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-38", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 38, "raw_text": "38. 根據本文，下列敘述何者正確？\n    (A)「封」和「禪」在同一處進行    (B)封禪的目的是為天下萬民祈福\n    (C)物富民豐的年代才會舉行封禪    (D)舉行封禪的皇帝未必賢德英明\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-039", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "秦二世封禪石刻所用的字體，與下列何者最接近？", "options": ["", "", "", ""], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-38", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": ["option_incomplete", "option_image"], "parse_confidence": 0.4, "original_question_number": 39, "raw_text": "39. 秦二世封禪石刻所用的字體，與下列何者最接近？\n    (A)      (B)     (C)          (D)\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": false, "auto_gradable": false, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-040", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，藥廠生產藥物的原則為下列何者？", "options": ["以民眾的需求為考量", "以疾病的輕重為依據", "以政府的規定為準則", "以利潤的追求為優先"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-40", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 40, "raw_text": "40. 根據本文，藥廠生產藥物的原則為下列何者？\n    (A)以民眾的需求為考量    (B)以疾病的輕重為依據\n    (C)以政府的規定為準則    (D)以利潤的追求為優先\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-041", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，無法推知下列何者？", "options": ["治療蛇毒的抗蛇毒血清利潤不夠高", "利潤愈來愈低，所以藥廠越來越少", "天花疫苗原本的標準接種次數不只一次", "美國 疾管局建議延期注射是因為疫苗供應不足"], "correct_answer": 1, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-40", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 41, "raw_text": "41. 根據本文，無法推知下列何者？\n    (A)治療蛇毒的抗蛇毒血清利潤不夠高\n    (B)利潤愈來愈低，所以藥廠越來越少\n    (C)天花疫苗原本的標準接種次數不只一次\n    (D)美國 疾管局建議延期注射是因為疫苗供應不足\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-042", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據作者的觀點，下列行為何者屬於文明人的象徵？", "options": ["晚上在旅館小聲說話", "在戲院看演員演啞劇", "在鄉間見面時大聲問好", "被人踩住脖子時大喊救命"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-42", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 42, "raw_text": "42. 根據作者的觀點，下列行為何者屬於文明人的象徵？\n    (A)晚上在旅館小聲說話    (B)在戲院看演員演啞劇\n    (C)在鄉間見面時大聲問好   (D)被人踩住脖子時大喊救命\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}]'::jsonb) AS t(
